title: Hezbollah gains in Lebanon election
text:
Hezbollah gains in Lebanon election 2:28pm BST - 01:22
Hezbollah and its allies have won more than half the seats in Lebanon's election, unofficial results show, underscoring Iran's reach. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
